title: Episode 59 - Prelude to the Korean War
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary: Re-Recorded. Join us as we began our examination of the Korean War. In this episode, we outline a brief history of Korea leading up to the outbreak of the Korean War. We also examine how the failed US occupation contributed to the origins of the war.
